overview: 1st Choice Superseal Ltd deals in installation of new roofs, security products and in repairing or maintaining existing roofs. The company specialises in all types of domestic, commercial or industrial roofing and offers its installation and maintenance services in GRP roofing, flat roofing, pitched roofing, skylights, gutters, fascias, soffits, slating, tiling, chimneys, cladding, bollards, rollershutters, expanding grilles, fixed grilles, fencing and gates etc. It’s head office is in Great Barr, Birmingham and also cater to the needs of people residing in Lichfield, Solihull, Sutton Coldfield and areas surrounding them.
